DIDZTEKCAEA XJHKX TE RTENX HKEQEGEAIKE, KXOTXGEAE XJ XT XJHCXKKI PZTHCHZACJEKCI XJ QEKRXTIJE XT 22 AX JIvCXPQKX AX 1936, 
